bug.short_desc: Make user message about unavailable platforms less scary

assigned_to.name: Nobody; OK to take it and work on it

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 524218 screenshot
steps to reproduce: 1. Load https://addons.allizom.org/en-US/developers/addon/submit/2 2. Upload a mobile-only add-on. 3. Notice that desktop platforms are disabled with user message 'Some platforms are not available for this type of add-on' message
observed behavior: User message is in red and looks like an error message (see screenshot). We should use the new notification styling with the proper info icon.
